\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Resource Usage Trajectory. Average per-client GPU resource consumption (GB) across paradigm-complexity stages. Federated settings produce a clear 3--4$\times $ reduction in per-client resource usage relative to centralized training because each client holds only a data partition. LoRA further halves resource demands.}}{8}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:resource_trajectory}{{3}{8}{Resource Usage Trajectory. Average per-client GPU resource consumption (GB) across paradigm-complexity stages. Federated settings produce a clear 3--4$\times $ reduction in per-client resource usage relative to centralized training because each client holds only a data partition. LoRA further halves resource demands}{figure.caption.5}{}}
